# Cloudflare Pages redirects — served as true HTTP 301 before any static
# asset is looked up. The Astro-generated meta-refresh HTML files at
# /notes/index.html and /notes/<slug>/index.html remain as a fallback for
# any host that doesn't honour _redirects.
/notes            /thinking            301
/notes/*          /thinking/:splat     301
/uses             /kit                 301
